## NAMING CONVENTIONS

Classes:
  - Experiments:  [Name]Experiment         → RenderScaleExperiment
  - Metrics:      [Name]MetricProvider      → UnityStatsMetricProvider
  - Data models:  [Name]Metrics / [Name]Result
  - Interfaces:   I[Name]                   → IExperiment, IExperimentRunner
  - UI:           [Name]Panel / [Name]Controller

Files:
  - One class per file, filename matches class name exactly.
  - Interfaces live in Core/Interfaces/
  - Experiments live in Experiments/
  - Metrics live in Metrics/
  - UI scripts live in UI/

Namespaces:
  - XRLab.Core
  - XRLab.Experiments
  - XRLab.Metrics
  - XRLab.UI

