## EXPERIMENT CHECKLIST

When creating a new experiment, it MUST:
  [ ] Implement IExperiment (Name, Setup, Run, Teardown)
  [ ] Save original state in a private field during Setup()
  [ ] Restore original state in Teardown() (inside try/finally at call site)
  [ ] Modify only ONE performance variable
  [ ] Be registered in Bootstrap (not auto-discovered via reflection)
  [ ] Have an XML doc comment explaining what variable it tests
  [ ] Work in Unity Editor (use mock/editor fallback if XR not present)

---

## METRICS CHECKLIST

When creating a new metric provider, it MUST:
  [ ] Implement IMetricProvider
  [ ] Return a PerformanceMetrics value object (immutable)
  [ ] Handle null/unavailable stats gracefully (return 0, not throw)
  [ ] Be safe to call every frame from Update()
  [ ] Dispose of any ProfilerRecorder in OnDestroy

