## GIT CONVENTIONS

Branch naming:
  - feature/[name]     → feature/msaa-experiment
  - fix/[name]         → fix/teardown-null-ref
  - docs/[name]        → docs/architecture-update
  - refactor/[name]    → refactor/metrics-layer

Commit messages:
  - Format: [scope]: short description
  - Scopes: core | experiment | metrics | ui | docs | ci | refactor | fix
  - Examples:
      experiment: add MSAAExperiment with 4 quality levels
      metrics: add GPU frame time via ProfilerRecorder
      ui: add experiment control panel with run/stop buttons
      docs: update ARCHITECTURE.md with metrics flow diagram
  - Keep subject line under 72 characters.
  - Reference issue/task in body if applicable.

Do NOT commit:
  - Unity Library/ folder
  - .DS_Store, Thumbs.db
  - Build output folders
  - Any file with hardcoded device paths or API keys

